==生涯==
[[File:Nikki_Benz_2009.jpg|thumb]]
妮琪·班茲在21歲生日後不久結識成人影片導演，從此進入成人業界。她在2003年1月與 Pleasure Productions 簽下合約，與[[吉娜·琳|吉娜·琳]]拍攝第一部性愛場景（《Strap On Sally 20》）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://business.avn.com/articles/10333.html | title=Pleasure: A Case of the Benz | accessdate=2007-09-23 | date=2003-01-28 | publisher=[[成人影帶新聞|AVN]] | pages=1 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090523154758/http://business.avn.com/articles/10333.html | archivedate=2009-05-23 }}</ref>，再與知名男星[[班·英格利許|班·英格利許]]（Ben English）拍攝第一部男女性愛場景（《The Sweetest Thing》）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.avn.com/index.cfm?objectID=ED9C09B9-1372-4B41-C47FB92F8A96AE5C&slid=83632|title=A Boff at the Burger Palace: On the Set with Pleasure Girl Nikki Benz|accessdate=2007-09-23|author=Dan Miller|date=2003-01-28|publisher=[[成人影帶新聞|AVN]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030207052605/http://www.avninsider.com/stories/dm12703.shtml|archivedate=2003-02-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref> 合約期滿後，班茲前往[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，於2004年9月與[[吉兒·凱莉|吉兒·凱莉]]製作公司簽下合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/17915.html|title=Nikki Benz Signs On With Jill Kelly Productions|accessdate=2007-09-23|author=Ron Martin|date=2004-09-21|publisher=[[成人影帶新聞|AVN]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130117125056/http://business.avn.com/articles/17915.html|archivedate=2013-01-17}}</ref>
2005年9月，她與 TeraVision 簽約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://business.avn.com/articles/23022.html|title=Tera Vision Signs Nikki Benz and Lucy Lee|accessdate=2007-09-23|date=2005-09-08|publisher=[[成人影帶新聞|AVN]]|archive-date=2013-01-17|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130117111106/http://business.avn.com/articles/23022.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

班茲曾拍攝許多知名成人雜誌，如《[[閣樓_(雜誌)|閣樓]]》、《{{tsl|en|High Society (magazine)|上流社會 (雜誌)|上流社會}}》、《{{tsl|en|Genesis (magazine)|創世紀 (雜誌)|創世紀}}》、《{{tsl|en|Oui (magazine)|Oui (雜誌)|Oui}}》、《Cheri》、《[[好色客|好色客]]》、《{{tsl|en|Club (magazine)|俱樂部 (雜誌)|俱樂部}}》、《{{tsl|en|Club International (magazine)|俱樂部國際版 (雜誌)|俱樂部國際版}}》。她為2004年4月閣樓寵物，並曾是閣樓雜誌2008年5月的封面女郎。<ref name=pet>{{cite web|url = http://business.avn.com/articles/37583.html|title = Nikki Benz is April Penthouse Pet of the Month|accessdate = 2010-03-23|date = 2010-03-17|publisher = ''[[成人影帶新聞|AVN]]''|archive-date = 2010-04-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100430004602/http://business.avn.com/articles/37583.html|dead-url = no}}</ref> 班茲被選為閣樓雜誌2011年年度寵物。<ref name=petoftheyear>{{cite web|url=http://penthousemagazine.com/issues/2011/penthouse-magazine-january-2011/|title=Penthousemagazine.com|accessdate=5 January 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101227195754/http://penthousemagazine.com/issues/2011/penthouse-magazine-january-2011/|archivedate=2010年12月27日}}</ref>

